title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Mitsubishi Pajero 3.2L 4M41 2010-on – Fuel Manager Pre-Filter Kit / pairs with Provent Catch Can Dual Bracket Kit OS-38-FM

content.rendered:
Fuel Manager Pre-Filter Kit

Mitsubishi Pajero 3.2L 4M41 2010-on

DI-D CRD Turbo Diesel

*** Requires DUAL Bracket Companion Kit OS-PROV-38B to Install ***

Kit SKUs followed by the letter ‘B’ include Bracket / FM = Fuel Manager Pre-Filter

OS-38-FMB: (Fuel Manager Pre-Filter + Bracket)

OS-38-FM (Fuel Manager Pre-Filter ONLY)

OS-PROV-38: (Provent ONLY)

Ideal Companion for this kit:

OS-PROV-38B: (Provent + Bracket)

This Fuel Manager Pre-Filter Kit can be installed alongside the Western Filters Provent Catch Can Dual Bracket Kit. Utilising one bracket for two very important uses and protecting your vehicle !

Fuel Manager Benefits:

Fuel Manager is a unique, patented, modular diesel fuel filter/water separator system that can be customized for virtually any application. Each employ unique fiLation process, trapping more impurities and water without impeding the flow rate. The product’s design permits the replacement of elements without the use of tools and without spilling fuel, making service easy in the shop or in the field. When an element is replaced, an easily opened drain valve allows the filter to be completely and neatly emptied before it is removed.

Download PDF Installation Instructions >
